  "prompt": "What is the average and highest package of Galgotia University Noida?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, the average and highest placement packages for students from Galgotias University in Noida can vary by year and by program. Generally speaking, engineering and computer science graduates tend to secure higher packages compared to other programs. \n\nOn average, students from the university might expect packages in the range of 3 to 6 lakhs per annum, while top performers and those in high-demand fields such as computer science can sometimes receive packages upwards of 10 to 15 lakhs per annum or higher.\n\nFor the most accurate and current information regarding placement statistics, including average and highest packages, it's best to check the university's official website or contact their placement cell directly, as these figures can change from year to year and depend on various factors including industry demand and the job market.",
